---
---
<section class="contact" id="contact">
  <div class="contact-inner">
    <div class="contact-left">
      <span class="label">Start a Project</span>
      <h2 class="contact-title">
        LET'S TALK<br/>
        ABOUT WHAT<br/>
        YOU'RE<br/>
        <span class="accent">WORKING AROUND</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-right">
      <p class="contact-body">
        If there's a process in your organization that relies on a workaround
        — a spreadsheet, a manual step, a tool that only partially fits —
        that is the right place to start.
      </p>
      <p class="contact-body">
        Send us a description of the problem. We'll respond with an honest
        assessment of what a custom solution would involve.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@pixelcraft.dev" class="contact-cta">
        <span class="cta-label label">Send us a message</span>
        <span class="cta-main">hello@pixelcraft.dev</span>
        <span class="cta-hint label">Response within 24 hours</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <span class="label">© 2024 Pixelcraft</span>
    <span class="label">Custom Enterprise Software</span>
    <span class="label">pixelcraft.dev</span>
  </footer>
</section>

<style>
  .contact {
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .contact-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .contact-left {
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    border-right: var(--border-inv);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .contact-left .label { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .contact-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-h2);
    color: var(--color-text-inv);
  }

  .contact-right {
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .contact-body {
    max-width: 42ch;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .contact-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    border: var(--border-inv);
    padding: var(--space);
    width: fit-content;
    color: var(--color-text-inv);
    margin-top: var(--space);
  }

  .contact-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .cta-main {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .site-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space) var(--space-lg);
    border-top: var(--border-inv);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .contact-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: var(--border-inv); padding: var(--space-lg); }
    .contact-right { padding: var(--space-lg); }
    .site-footer { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--space); }
  }
</style>
